title: I Didn't Make a Plan
lyrics:
Didn't make a plan
To break your heart
But it was the sweetest thing
I've ever done
Didn't need a plan

I just need a body

I put it on the line

And I won



No more the tool

Off daddy's back

The water, it just blended

With the wine



Now all the tongues

Of every sailor

In aims just to place

To raise the wire



Hey, oh

Hey, oh

Hey, oh

Hey, oh



Hey, oh

Hey, oh

Hey, oh

Hey, oh
